reviewText:
I paid less then $6 for this and it was a great deal. The only thing about this order was that it is not a DVD, but a Blu-Ray, I really don't have a problem with this since I own a Blu-Ray player, but those who don't own one, may take issue.

The Blu-Ray itself was in great shape and played perfectly.
The description was a DVD but it was Blu-ray.  Could not view on my DVD player so I returned it.
